==Usage== <!--T:6-->

<!--T:7-->
# Select one or more objects.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View → [[Image:Std_SetMaterial.svg|16px]] Material}} option from the menu.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Std_SetMaterial.svg|16px]] Material}} option from the [[Tree_View|Tree View]] context menu or [[3D_View|3D View]] context menu.
# The '''Material''' task panel opens.
# If required click on the down arrow to the right of the current material to show the full task panel.
# Select a material from the list.
## Optionally press the {{Button|Launch Editor}} button to launch the [[Material_Edit|Material Editor]].
# The objects are updated immediately.
# Optionally select one or more new objects whose material you want to change.
# Press the {{Button|Close}} button to close the task panel and finish the command.


